- Use `describe` and `it` blocks to organize your tests
- Implement mocking with `vi.mock` for isolating dependencies
- Use Vitest's concurrent test running feature for faster test execution
- Leverage Vitest's code coverage reporting to ensure thorough test coverage
- Implement proper mocking of dependencies using Vitest's mocking utilities
- Utilize `vitest.run` for running tests programmatically
- Leverage `vitest`'s snapshot testing for UI components
- Utilize Vitest's watch mode for efficient test-driven development
